FBIS3-16854 "drsov054_a_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-054 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Mar 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Kozyrev Urges DPRK Compliance OW2103123394 Tokyo KYODO in English 1216 GMT 21 Mar 94 OW2103123394 Tokyo KYODO Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Moscow, March 21 KYODO -- Russian Foreign Minister Andrey Kozyrev urged North Korea on Monday [21 March] to abide by controls on nuclear facilities as imposed under the international nuclear safeguard agreement, Japanese officials said. During a meeting with Japanese Foreign Minister Tsutomu Hata, Kozyrev argued that all controls should be abided by through inspections by experts from the International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA), the officials said. [passage omitted]
